            "jpName": "メジロマックイーン",
            "enName": "Mejiro McQueen",
            "jpText": "……この夏で、淀を走りきる力は\n十分に備わったと思います。ですが――",
            "enText": "…I believe we have surpassed our training \nexpectations for this summer, and are \nprepared for whatever may come. \nHowever…",
