        {
            "jpName": "ステイゴールド",
            "enName": "Stay Gold",
            "jpText": "浮かれる余裕なんてないさ。\n夏明けの景色は、まるで別物だからな。\n……かつてお前が示したように。",
            "enText": "There's no time for festivities. It's like how \nyou've shown me before in the past… \nThe scenery after summer is that of a \ncompletely different beast.",
