        {
            "jpName": "マチカネフクキタル",
            "enName": "Matikanefukukitaru",
            "jpText": "『菊花賞』！　今現在上り調子の\nこのマチカネフクキタルがステゴさんに\n勝たせていただきますからっ！！",
            "enText": "It's the Kikuka Sho! This very up and \ncoming Matikanefukukitaru shall at \nthis very moment declare her victory \nagainst you, Stego!!",
