            "jpName": "マチカネフクキタル",
            "enName": "Matikanefukukitaru",
            "jpText": "やりました！\nステゴさんが宣言を受け止めてくれたので、\nますます私の運気が爆上昇です！！",
            "enText": "I did it! To think Stego would even accept \nmy declaration, I can feel my fortunes \nare exploding sky high right now!!",
